README:
Proof of genral Tarai function termination problem.

This proof highly bases on Ishiu's proof "http://arxiv.org/abs/1007.0467".

Files

 * Tarai_Base.v: Defition of general Tarai function.
 * Denotation.v: Facts from denotational semantics.
 * Util.v: Utility lemmas.
 * Tarai.v: Main theorem.
description: Proof of general Tarai function termination problem by Coq
